            "description": "<p>Join us for our end-of-year social + Senior Send-Off \ud83c\udf93\u2728<br /><br />We&rsquo;re closing out the year with a cozy celebration for our TWN community, especially our graduating seniors. Come hang out, take photos, grab snacks, and toast to everything you&rsquo;ve accomplished this year.<br /><br />Whether you&rsquo;re graduating or coming back next year, this is your chance to celebrate our seniors and spend time with friends before summer starts!</p>",
